OL,3,CCardiff City star admits abusing
OL,4,Cpolice officer and drink driving
OL,6,FA footballer has been banned from
OL,7,Fdriving after admitting to drink
OL,8,Fdriving and abusing police officer in
OL,9,Fthe earlier this year.
OL,11,FMahlon Romeo, 28, was handed a 14-
OL,12,Fmonth ban from driving at Magistrates
OL,13,FCourt on Monday, after pleading guilty
OL,14,Fto a drink driving offence on Cefn
OL,15,FCoed Road in February.
OL,17,FRomeo was found to have 58 micro grams
OL,18,Fof alcohol per 100 ml of breath. The
OL,19,Flegal limit is 35 micro grams.
