OL,6,FThe sentence comes one month after
OL,7,Fmanager Erol Bulut revealed the
OL,8,Fdefender had been disciplined by the
OL,9,Fclub. Bulut declined to expand on the
OL,10,Fdetails, describing the move as an
OL,11,F"internal" issue.
OL,13,FBulut explained: "I said at the start
OL,14,Fof the season, discipline and respect
OL,15,Fis the most important thing for me."
